{"tid":1154664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"觀塘官立小學集體食物中毒　10小學生疑進食內地零食後不適送院 ","createTime":"2019-05-14T12:23:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T13:00:55.000Z","uid":40152,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6a02f06c9fe541ceab0b2a838ebf1ea06c246dac","tid":1154664,"uid":40152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T12:23:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vAOUQo4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvAOUQo4.jpg&h=b89da366&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中午12時半，秀茂坪觀塘官立小學（秀明道）有10名學生懷疑進食不潔食物，部分人不適嘔吐，校方報警，救護員到場為5男5女學生檢查後送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指出，其中一名不適的學生早前曾到內地，購入一包「無窮愛辣雞米」作手信與同學分享，詎料引起懷疑集體食物中毒事故。<br />\n該校副校長陳玉珍接受查詢時表示，該10名六年級學生同於小息時進食一包在校外購買的肉乾零食，其後3名學生不適嘔吐，校方召救護車到場把不適同學送院。陳副校稱，由於慎重起見，其餘7名有份進食零食的同學亦一併送院檢查。校方現已通知涉事學生家長。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190514/s00001/1557815243652/%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98%E5%AE%98%E7%AB%8B%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E9%9B%86%E9%AB%94%E9%A3%9F%E7%89%A9%E4%B8%AD%E6%AF%92-10%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E7%96%91%E9%80%B2%E9%A3%9F%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E9%9B%B6%E9%A3%9F%E5%BE%8C%E4%B8%8D%E9%81%A9%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190514%2Fs00001%2F1557815243652%2F%25E8%25A7%2580%25E5%25A1%2598%25E5%25AE%2598%25E7%25AB%258B%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E9%259B%2586%25E9%25AB%2594%25E9%25A3%259F%25E7%2589%25A9%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%25AF%2592-10%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2596%2591%25E9%2580%25B2%25E9%25A3%259F%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E9%259B%25B6%25E9%25A3%259F%25E5%25BE%258C%25E4%25B8%258D%25E9%2581%25A9%25E9%2580%2581%25E9%2599%25A2&d=%2Bo3sOR8bLgAbrAMBqI8fZ%2BSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=5e47ede5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190514%2Fs00001%2F1557815243652%2F%25E8%25A7%2580%25E5%25A